            <p>
                Hello! I'm [Name], a passionate student with a wide range of interests. <strong>I love coding</strong> and exploring new technologies. In my free time, I enjoy <em>playing basketball</em> with my friends, and <em>traveling</em> to new places to experience different cultures. I'm also a huge fan of playing video games, especially strategy and puzzle games, which help me improve my problem-solving skills. I'm always eager to learn new things and embrace new challenges.
